  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add mustard seeds and fennel seeds to the pan. Stir for 2 minutes or until aromatic.",
    "Chop onion and garlic finely, add them to the pan with sliced ham. Sauté until soft, about 5 minutes.",
    "Pour in broth, bring to a simmer. Add rice and stir well to coat with the mixture.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover and cook for 18 minutes or until liquid is absorbed.",
    "Stir in white pepper before serving."
